  "text": "Utilizing energy-based cost function to identify biomechanical frameworks of biological tissue is yet another promising approach in material characterization. However, this method has not yet demonstrated the ability to quantitatively characterize parameters of interest, particularly long term shear modulus and time constant, in more relevant clinical settings [CITATION_1] .",
